parameters:
When I was a child, I used to love sitting on the fountain and
getting my skirt all wet. But now, I can't do that anymore, can
I?

Flyer distribution. No newspapers or religious solicitation.
...is written.
\SE[100] I can hear some noise... Should I listen carefully?

These vegetables were grown with love. During the harvest season,
they provide a huge supply.

\SE[51] (Actually, it's a secret that some of them have gone bad
because I couldn't eat them all.)

The clothes that got wet from playing in the water are becoming
see-through... It feels like they might be visible soon...

Huh, Laura? You were just looking at me with a sexual gaze,
weren't you?

\SM[slideb]\SE[18]I wasn't looking! I wasn't looking, okay?!
\SM[nod]\SE[8]No way... like that... haha...

\SE\SE[45]Huh... Could it be... Do you want to see Sakippo again?
\!\SE[45]
間に合ってますけどっ！？

\SE[4]Oh my... You're so honest, aren't you? \SE[51]Well, I guess
there's no helping it...
間に合ってますけどっ！？

\SE\SE[21]Lunaroa suddenly started saying that she wants to go to
school. It seems like her study motivation suddenly increased.
\SE[21]But, for us commoners, there's the entrance fee... I
wonder how we can manage this...

\SE[15]A girl playing in the water... \| \SM[tremble]\SE[42]Ah...
my heart feels fulfilled...
Ah, Laura big sister! Shall we play in the water together?

\SE\SE[0] Ah, big sister. \SE[0] Are you going to ventilate
again? Want to watch?
\SE[2]Is that so...? If that's the case, then it's fine...

\SE[1]Oh, are you taking a break...? \.You look tired from
playing in the water?

\SE[2]Ah... yeah. It's just that I started feeling like it's all
just a child's play... \SE[3]Suddenly, I started thinking that
it's all just pointless.

\SE[14]I have to do something more useful for the future!
\SE[13]Alright, from now on, let's study hard every day for the
future... Even a journey of a thousand miles begins with a single
step...

\SE[33]Give her back...! Return the innocent and pure Ronoa-
chan...!!

\SE[2] From now on, it's the era of individuals. Big sis. \SE[3]
I think it will be a time where being a strong individual who
doesn't rely on society will be demanded.

\SE[33]Give her back...! Return the innocent and pure Ronoa-
chan...!!

Sigh... Even though it's my day off, I've been entrusted with
babysitting...
\SE[1]Eh? Isn't it nice to have something cute?

Oh! Laura-chan! If you're interested, would you like to go out
and have a meal with me? There's also a beautiful place with a
night view.

It's bothersome to be approached by a guy like this, isn't it? It
feels like a waste of time and becomes 'stressful', right?

When that happens, let's try pressing the Ctrl button. You will
be able to quickly ignore bothersome conversations...! Let's blow
away tedious conversations!!
Let's make sure not to miss important conversations.

\SE[2]I'm in the middle of a quest, so it's impossible for me
right now.

Alright, I'll help. Let's finish quickly and go have some fun
somewhere, okay?

\SM[nod]\SE[12]Oops, I'm sorry. \.This is meant for one person
only.
Ugh! You're still as stubborn as ever with your guard...

Lately... I've been acting strange. When I realized it, I
couldn't help but keep looking at Melissa, and I can't seem to
speak properly anymore...

\SE[99]Oh...? By the way, have you ever thought about holding
hands... or going out together...? \SE[2]

...Just a little... I'm starting to feel restless... Something
feels strange.

\SE\SE[28]Wow... A step towards adulthood... \SE[28]It feels kind
of itchy watching this...

Even though I look at Laura, I don't feel anything... It's
strange.
It's so peaceful. I suppose this is what they call happiness...

Laura... It's not good to look at the children with such a
scornful gaze.

Ah, the branches are reaching all the way to the house. Looks
like I'll have to trim them...

\SE[44]It's the grave of the dog that a single uncle used to own.
It passed away not too long ago...

\SE[24]She was a troublesome girl who often charged into my
skirt, but now that she's gone... I can't help but feel lonely.

Warm sunlight! Clear air! Refreshing breeze! On such a wonderful
day...
I want to relax without working...!!
A sign for a single uncle's marriage hunting.

I am a single uncle 🎵😃♥ Looking for a marriage partner, so please
contact me if interested, na 😆 Let's go out for a meal on
Saturday or something, yo⁉😃 (laughs)
\SE[16]Ahaha! It's Laura's fault for getting in the way!
\SE[16]Ahaha!! Big sis, you're doing it on purpose, aren't you?!

\SE[12]\SM[double]No, Bashaa!...!? \SE[33]Those two are the ones
who will pour water on us!!?

\SE[2]Isn't it about time we stop doing things like that...?
\SE[3]We can't keep playing around forever, especially at our
age...
\SE[2]... But you know, children grow up so fast, don't they...
The village girl Laura was excited by a single letter.
